data.description: This well-maintained home offers comfortable living and an incredible outdoor oasis. Step inside to discover ceramic tile floors throughout and stylish zebra curtains. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with a newer aluminum roof (2017), A/C system, including ducts(2017), and impact windows & doors (2018)   The true highlight is the backyard paradise. Cool off in the sparkling pool, enjoy the playground, and relax in the shade provided by a mature lychee tree. A convenient shed offers extra storage space.   This home is perfect for buyers seeking a move-in-ready property with a fantastic outdoor living space. Don't miss this opportunity – schedule your showing today!
